"label":"Stabilsers underway"},{"label":"Watermakers"},{"label":"Flybridge"}],"entertainment":["4/5G Internet","Bluetooth speakers/sounds system conn.","Outdoor sound system","Starlink","TV in all cabins","TV in saloon","WiFi connection"]},"crew":[{"name":"Elie Makhlouf","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::938c8ca0-08e9-11f1-bc12-458f582189be::assets::b85d42a0-08f7-11f1-9940-81a943bd1c58/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Lebanese\n\nDiesel engine studies at Kartboun School; yacht travel since 2015 across the Mediterranean and Red Sea regions.\n\nI grew up around yachts, my older brother is a captain, so I was introduced to the yachting lifestyle from a very young age. I started working in the industry at 16 and have been passionate about the sea and yacht life ever since."},{"name":"Jhon B. Rotubio","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::938c8ca0-08e9-11f1-bc12-458f582189be::assets::bb1de940-08f7-11f1-9940-81a943bd1c58/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Filipino\n\nI am a Bachelor of Science in Nautical Studies graduate with a strong foundation in navigation, maritime safety, and ship operations. My training and travels have strengthened my discipline, teamwork, and adaptability. I’m passionate about pursuing a professional maritime career and contributing to safe and efficient vessel operations.\n\nI have hands-on experience working on ships, where I gained practical knowledge of navigation, vessel operations, and maritime safety. My time at sea inspired me to pursue a career in yachting, as I wanted to combine my maritime expertise with the dynamic, guest-focused environment that the yachting industry offers."},{"name":"Mikhael Mattar","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::938c8ca0-08e9-11f1-bc12-458f582189be::assets::be102730-08f7-11f1-9940-81a943bd1c58/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Lebanese\n\nI joined the Lebanese Army at the age of 16, where I developed a strong sense of discipline, teamwork, and responsibility. During my time in service, I also pursued my passion for swimming and became the Lebanese Open Water Swimming Champion for the years 2017–2018 and 2018–2019. \nGrowing up in a coastal family, I spent much of my childhood at sea. My father is a fisherman, and I often sailed with him, learning practical seamanship and respect for the ocean from an early age. My cousin works on a yacht, and I gained valuable hands-on experience assisting him on board. After several years of service, I decided to follow my passion for the maritime world and transitioned into the yachting industry. I officially left the Lebanese Army on March 21, 2024, to pursue a professional career at sea, combining my military discipline, swimming expertise, and lifelong experience on boats.\n\nI grew up at sea with my fisherman father and gained experience on yachts with my cousin. As Lebanon’s open water swimming champion (2017–2019), I developed a deep passion for the ocean and chose yachting as my career."},{"name":"Nataliya Sfeir","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::938c8ca0-08e9-11f1-bc12-458f582189be::assets::c16ebb80-08f7-11f1-9940-81a943bd1c58/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Ukrainian\n\nI graduated from the Institute of Tourism, Economics, and Law in Kyiv with a bachelor’s degree in law. I am divorced and have three children — two sons and a daughter. I have traveled all over Europe and discovered many countries, including Italy, Greece, and Spain, which has allowed me to experience and appreciate diverse cultures and traditions.\n\nAlthough I did not grow up around boats, my interest in the yachting industry developed through my appreciation for travel, hospitality, and service excellence. Over time, I was drawn to the professionalism, precision, and discipline that the yachting environment requires. I enjoy working in a professional and international environment, where teamwork, organization, and dedication are key, and where I can grow both personally and professionally."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":9000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":9000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":11000000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":11000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":9000000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":9000000,"amount":9000000,"taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.2},"conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded"},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.35,"unitPrice":9000000,"amount":3150000}],"total":13950000,"subTotal":12150000,"totalTax":1800000},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"France","type":"Country","category":["Europe","Western Europe","France"],"coordinates":[-3.676762491181631,13.257370810531999],"bbox":[-61.79784094999991,-21.37078215899993,55.854502800000034,51.08754088371883]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"High Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":11000000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":11000000,"amount":11000000,"conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.2}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"","quantity":0.35,"unitPrice":11000000,"amount":3849999.9999999995}],"total":17050000,"s